headline: Invitation Homes Announces Dual Listing On NYSE Texas
summary: DALLAS, August 14, 2025--Invitation Homes Inc. (NYSE: INVH) ("Invitation Homes," the "Company," or "our") announced today the dual listing of its common stock on NYSE Texas, the newly launched, fully electronic equities exchange headquartered in Dallas, Texas.
